'''Jean-Michel Vernhes''', born in 1950 at [[Mazamet]], is a [[France|French]] [[public servant]]. He is the current President of French Airports (''Union des a<U+00E9>roports fran<U+00E7>ais'') and of [[Toulouse-Blagnac Airport]]<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.toulouse.aeroport.fr/fr/content/jean-michel-vernhes-pr-sident-du-directoire-2 Jean-Michel Vernhes - Pr<U+00E9>sident du Directoire]</ref><ref>{{fr}}[http://www.objectifnews.com/business/resultats-aeroport-toulouse-trafic-2011-26012012 L'interview de 18h. Jean-Michel Vernhes, A<U+00E9>roport de Toulouse-Blagnac : "Une croissance de 9,1% en 2011"]</ref>.

== Biography ==
Graduate from ''[[classes pr<U+00E9>paratoires aux grandes <U+00E9>coles]]'' at Lyc<U+00E9>e Pierre de Fermat (Toulouse) and from the ''[[<U+00C9>cole nationale de l'aviation civile]]'' (French civil aviation university, promotion 1971<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.ingenac.fr/annuaire.php Annuaire]</ref>), Jean-Michel Vernhes starts his career in 1975 at the [[Air traffic control|air traffic control center]] of [[Bordeaux]]<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.ladepeche.fr/article/2011/06/12/1105062-jean-michel-vernhes-monsieur-aeroport.html Jean-Michel Vernhes, Monsieur a<U+00E9>roport]</ref>. In 1980, he moves to Paris where he is responsible for the certification of [[radio navigation]] equipments<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.aeroport.fr/bio_president.htm Le pr<U+00E9>sident de l'UAF : Jean-Michel VERNHES]</ref>. In 1986, he becomes President of the [[Nouvelle-Cal<U+00E9>donie]] [[air navigation]] center<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.ladepeche.fr/article/2010/01/19/758128-jean-michel-vernhes-un-pilote-a-l-aeroport.html Jean-Michel Vernhes, un pilote <U+00E0> l'a<U+00E9>roport]</ref>. He comes back to Paris in 1989 to work until 1993 at the [[aircraft]] certification department. In 1993, he becomes responsible of [[human resources]] at the [[France|French]] [[air navigation]] service before being nominated President of [[Toulouse-Blagnac Airport]] in 1999.

The 18th of May 2011, in addition, he become President of the French Airports (''Union des a<U+00E9>roports fran<U+00E7>ais'')<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.leparisien.fr/toulouse-31000/jean-michel-vernhes-toulouse-blagnac-elu-president-des-aeroports-francais-18-05-2011-1455863.php Jean-Michel Vernhes (Toulouse-Blagnac) <U+00E9>lu pr<U+00E9>sident des a<U+00E9>roports fran<U+00E7>ais]</ref><ref>{{fr}}[http://www.objectifnews.com/business/vernhes-aeroport-toulouse-blagnac-uaf-19052011 Jean-Michel Vernhes <U+00E9>lu <U+00E0> la t<U+00EA>te de l<U+2019>Union des a<U+00E9>roports fran<U+00E7>ais]</ref>.

== Award ==
* Officier of the [[L<U+00E9>gion d'honneur]]<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.ingenac.fr/UserFiles/File/Lettre_INGENAC_automne06%20VOK.pdf Association des Ing<U+00E9>nieurs et des Mast<U+00E8>res de l'<U+00C9>cole nationale de l'aviation civile]</ref><ref>{{fr}}[http://www.lourdes-infos.com/CCIT_flashs/FP060721.pdf Jean-Michel Vernhes Chevalier de la L<U+00E9>gion d'honneur]</ref>

